<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<p>The India &amp; South Asia Studies Minor is an interdisciplinary minor that enables students to learn about the history, culture, society, religion, gender relations, media, political economy, international relations, urbanism, migration and diaspora, and languages and literatures of India and South Asia across regional and national boundaries. The India and South Asia Studies Minor is open to undergraduates in all four colleges.</p>
<h2>Minor Advisor</h2>
<p><a href="https://mesa.ucdavis.edu/advising-office">Middle East/South Asia Studies Advising Office</a></p>
]]>
</informationtext>
