<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The interdisciplinary <span class="title-main">India &amp; South Asia Studies </span>minor, open to undergraduates in all four colleges, covers an area of immense historical, cultural, economic, demographic, and geopolitical significance. The minor is designed to emphasize the interconnected and comparative aspects of the area across regional and national boundaries.</p>
